    <span class="nuvo_bold">T&acirc;puaki</span>, Togan for "blessing", lets you fulfil the needs of teachers in the developing world. In return you receive a token of appreciation from those you helped.
  </p>
  <p>Charity making a real and tangible impact.
  </p>
  <p>
    Created to help progress the <%= link_to "United Nations' Millennium Goal of Universal Education", "http://www.un.org/millenniumgoals/education.shtml" %>, <span class="nuvo_bold">T&acirc;puaki</span> aims to ensure that children across the globe have equal access to resources.
  </p>
</div>
